&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1960 indian bollywood drama film directed by manmohan desai . it stars raj kapoor , nutan , pran , rehman and shobhna samarth . raj kapoor plays his stereotyped " simple guy with a heart of gold " role yet again . the story is loosely based on the " white nights " written by fyodor dostoyevsky but is focused on the issue of estranged wives and children in the aftermath of partition . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; was shot in black-and-white . music by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , played a part in the film 's box office success .